  (text "RPi5 INTERFACE NOTES:\\nJ_GPIO40: 40-pin 2x20 2.54mm (RPi5 compatible)\\n  Pins 1/17: +3V3. Pins 2/4: +5V. Pins 27/28: HAT EEPROM ID_SD/ID_SC\\n  STM32U585 signals: 3.3V direct\\n  QRB2210 GPIO: 1.8V → TXS0108E → 3.3V on header\\nHAT EEPROM U_EEPROM (24C32 SOIC-8):\\n  Address 0x50 (A0=A1=A2=GND). Pins 27/28 only.\\n  4.7kΩ pullups R_E2/R_E3 to +3V3 on ID_SD/ID_SC\\n  Program at first boot with RPi HAT EEPROM utilities\\nCSI FPC connectors: RPi5 camera ribbon cable compatible\\n  CCI (I2C): camera control → STM32U585 I2C4 (separate from GPIO bus)\\nNo PCIe: QRB2210 silicon has no PCIe root complex\\n  RPi5 NVMe HATs incompatible with this carrier"
    (at 20 155 0)
